<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Document</title>
  <style>
    body>* {
      /* border: 2px solid blue; */
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --grid-info-size: 350px;
      --color-bg-hg: lightgray;
    }

    html,
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    body {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-areas:
        "social info   content"
        "footer footer footer";
      grid-template-columns: auto var(--grid-info-size) 1fr;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 50px;
      gap: .5rem;
      padding: .5rem;
      min-height: 100svh;
    }

    aside {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;

      grid-area: info;

      .thumb {
        width: calc(var(--grid-info-size) - 20px);
        height: calc(var(--grid-info-size) - 20px);
        background-color: lightgray;
        border-radius: 50%;
        flex: none;
        z-index: 2;
        overflow: clip;

        img {
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          object-fit: cover;
        }
      }

      section {
        background-color: var(--color-bg-hg);
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        margin-top: -4rem;
        padding-top: 4rem;
        z-index: 1;
        clip-path: polygon(0 20px, 0 100%, 100% 100%, 100% 0);
      }
    }

    main {
      grid-area: content;
      position: relative;
      isolation: isolate;
      padding: 2rem;

      h1 {
        font-size: 4rem;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      &:before {
        content: "";
        background-color: var(--color-bg-hg);
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: -1;
        clip-path: polygon(0 calc(var(--grid-info-size) - 5.3rem),
            0 100%,
            100% 100%,
            100% calc(var(--grid-info-size) - 10rem));
      }

      .gallery {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        grid-auto-rows: minmax(180px, 230px);
        gap: .5rem;

        img {
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          object-fit: cover;
        }

        :first-child {
          grid-column: span 3;
          grid-row: span 2;
        }
      }
    }

    .social {
      grid-area: social;

      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;

      img {
        width: 2rem;
        height: 2rem;
        object-fit: cover;
      }
    }

    footer {
      grid-area: footer;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <aside>
    <div class="thumb">
      <img src="assets/thumb.png" alt="logo do maluco">
    </div>
    <section>aside</section>
  </aside>
  <main>
    <article>
      <h1>Article Title</h1>
      <p>
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec vel sapien eget
        nunc efficitur commodo. Sed ut perspiciatis unde omnis iste natus error sit
        voluptatem accusantium doloremque laudantium.
      </p>
    </article>
    <div class="gallery">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/1200/1200?1" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?2" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?3" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?4" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?5" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?6" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/400/300?7" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/300/200?8" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/250/200?9" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/300?10" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/600/200?11" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/350?12" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/300/200?13" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?14" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?15" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?16" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?17" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?18" alt="Image">
      <img src="https://picsum.photos/200/200?19" alt="Image">
    </div>
  </main>

  <div class="social">
    <a href="https://www.facebook.com">
      <img src="https://api.iconify.design/ph:facebook-logo-fill.svg" alt="Facebook">
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.twitter.com">
      <img src="https://api.iconify.design/ph:twitter-logo-fill.svg" alt="Twitter">
    </a>
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com">
      <img src="https://api.iconify.design/ph:instagram-logo-fill.svg" alt="Instagram">
    </a>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Niel. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>

</html>
